  <summary date="2021-04-07T19:39:13Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Continued Funding for Senior Services During COVID-19 Act

This bill provides additional funding for FY2021 to the Administration for Community Living for social services and programs for individuals aged 60 years or older, including to mitigate and prevent COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).

With respect to the additional funding, the bill waives matching requirements that typically apply to funding for these services and programs.</summary>
